ygData.messageBody:
Whow cleric is just great to have in group if you find any other you can go
to area just before slavers huts and hunt things there (DONT HIT SLAVERS
until with strong group) and you can hit orcs wich respawn near mountain
side and in slavers cave entrance and pull them to space near cave entrance
one plato in mountain side kill them there and rest then fetch another here
no trains pass and you can freely rest. Only be careful when you go to
fetch another victim ehehheh.
